new jack city is a 1991 american action gangster film based upon an original story and screenplay by thomas lee wright , and directed by mario van peebles in his directorial debut , who also co-stars in the film . the film stars wesley snipes , ice-t , allen payne , chris rock , mario van peebles and judd nelson . the film was released in the united states on march 8 , 1991 . wesley snipes plays nino brown , a rising drug dealer and crime lord in new york city during the crack epidemic . ice-t plays scotty appleton , a detective who vows to stop nino 's criminal activity by going undercover to work for nino 's gang .